**At EVERY session start, load in this order:**

1. **Core Governance** (MANDATORY - Always load):
   - @.cursor-commands/profiles/session-startup-protocol.md
   - @.cursor-commands/learning/repeated-mistakes.md
   - @.cursor-commands/learning/quick-fixes.md

2. **Task-Specific Profiles** (Load based on task type):
